-Den je mrtav!

00:48:46.447 --> 00:48:48.914
Šta se kog đavola dešava ovdje?!

00:48:49.917 --> 00:48:52.985
Reci mi ili se gubi!

00:49:03.430 --> 00:49:05.564
Kada sam imao 26...

00:49:08.269 --> 00:49:10.836
...otkrio sam,
da dok spavam...

00:49:12.306 --> 00:49:16.074
